title: File:South Korea, Incheon, Songdo (02), street scene.jpg
author: Vincent van Zeijst
description: Street scene with city bus in central Songdo (Yeonsu-gu district, Incheon, South-Korea). Street name is Convensia-daero 130beon-gil. On the left is one of the Prugio Central Park Towers with some of the Sharp Central Park Towers behind it.
